{"tid":1855113,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"千祈千祈千祈 文宣文宣文宣","createTime":"2020-02-01T02:03:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T14:35:26.000Z","uid":85924,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2f8ec4e692bd5260397506be9863006168697b70","tid":1855113,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T02:03:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地要令！呢場瘟瘟人禍！成為壓倒港共既最後一根稻草！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢場人禍會令民眾既不滿滋生到極點，時機一到將會再爆發，港府政府今次走唔甩！<br />\n<br />\n點做：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣！鋪天蓋地既文宣！</span></span>必然要將茅頭指向港共。<br />\n<br />\n港共三大罪：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes10.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes20.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不作為<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes50.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />囤口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes100.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n上次打足半年有多班藍絲都仲可以死撐港共政府，但我尋晚聽到屋企件藍絲話：一切都係林鄭搞出黎。證明今次人禍係足以connect all。<br />\n<br />\n而家集體運動未必搞到，但文宣絕對係現時威力最強既武器。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你見而家港共全力清文宣，甚至動用鄉黑打壓文宣就知，佢地絕對驚到瀨屎。而家全港文宣清得7788，我地就要同港共對著幹！動用一切力量搞旺文宣！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c9f6ad91da1171b2c9365ba09d152448b892e2","tid":1855113,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T02:03:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb265c9117a11cde41887664b64e5d82b805705e","tid":1855113,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T02:03:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"060afe079986ab43f5e2da73a3b8da35e2784678","tid":1855113,"uid":85924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T02:05:24.000Z","msg":"其實而家情況特殊，有好多創意方法可以玩，例如派口罩+文宣，等班藍絲谷住谷住咁攞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025132f0cb262898be48bab079c36fdc8615eea3","tid":1855113,"uid":85924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T02:07:18.000Z","msg":"長輩圖唔少得啦：你知道嗎？林鄭私藏幾千萬口罩....<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec0f7033565e3eafeb26e5549a80e50c766b375","tid":1855113,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T02:07:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da3359662c41cdd475d1246f20d0985b184b21d4","tid":1855113,"uid":85924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T02:08:18.000Z","msg":"集思廣益，發揮創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"316354bf6a21663b104dc86b01c38e39d9a5b16a","tid":1855113,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T02:08:59.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"e274d37d98e81b1d80599e426249956882ec9c5d","tid":1855113,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T02:11:50.000Z","msg":"田"},{"pid":"10aa2f337126e9c4ee64e2233c21faad2cbe2774","tid":1855113,"uid":265171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T02:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf8937bc0165f0734076c255e4815cf7107279d","tid":1855113,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T03:04:25.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"ed8e226e94194d0570bbb2cc0d452adef47446e1","tid":1855113,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f8ec4e692bd5260397506be9863006168697b70","tid":1855113,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T02:03:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地要令！呢場瘟瘟人禍！成為壓倒港共既最後一根稻草！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢場人禍會令民眾既不滿滋生到極點，時機一到將會再爆發，港府政府今次走唔甩！<br />\n<br />\n點做：<span style=\